WEBVTT

03:30.800 --> 03:35.380
At the very beginning we have to know that the truth is what it is.

03:36.000 --> 03:38.980
You cannot change it

03:39.500 --> 03:43.120
You cannot transform it

03:43.780 --> 03:49.140
And at this human awareness you cannot know it

04:00.140 --> 04:09.040
That means in our evolutionary process we have reached this state of a human being

04:09.360 --> 04:13.020
but it is not the end of our evolution

04:24.820 --> 04:30.920
because we don´t know what is Absolute truth.

04:33.760 --> 04:37.940
Whatever I´m going to tell you today

04:39.740 --> 04:43.860
you have to take it

04:47.020 --> 04:52.000
with an open mind like a scientist.

05:01.540 --> 05:04.140
If it is proved

05:04.780 --> 05:07.620
than you have to accept it as

05:08.160 --> 05:10.600
honest people.

05:14.940 --> 05:20.680
Because it is for your benevolence,

05:22.340 --> 05:25.140
it is for the benevolence of your country,

05:25.640 --> 05:28.600
it is for the benevolence of the whole world.

05:44.920 --> 05:51.280
So please listen to me carefully what I have to tell you.

06:07.260 --> 06:09.920
There is within us

06:10.920 --> 06:12.840
a power,

06:13.460 --> 06:17.020
which is placed in the triangular bone,

06:18.700 --> 06:21.580
for our ascend.

06:34.220 --> 06:39.280
It is for our last breakthrough.

06:41.900 --> 06:47.060
And this breakthrough has to happen

06:47.580 --> 06:52.220
as a process of our evolution.

06:57.540 --> 07:02.080
So the truth is that

07:02.480 --> 07:05.520
you are not this body,

07:05.840 --> 07:10.160
this mind, this ego, these conditionings.

07:10.560 --> 07:14.020
But you are the Pure Spirit.

07:25.300 --> 07:30.320
And the second truth is that there is

07:31.280 --> 07:36.100
a very subtle power of Divine Love

07:37.200 --> 07:47.120
that does all the living work.

07:56.600 --> 07:59.620
We see all these beautiful flowers all around us.

08:00.100 --> 08:07.640
But we don´t even think whatever a miracle it is.

08:13.680 --> 08:20.320
That out of one seed such beautiful flowers come out.

08:26.280 --> 08:28.360
Who runs your heart?

08:29.140 --> 08:34.200
The doctors may say it is the autonomous nervous system.

08:34.460 --> 08:36.160
Who is this auto?

08:48.580 --> 08:53.040
We go to science and we find that there

08:53.220 --> 08:56.340
are many questions which cannot be answered.

09:04.640 --> 09:07.780
Science cannot tell us why are we on this Earth.

09:13.400 --> 09:15.680
What is the purpose of life?

09:18.240 --> 09:22.500
What is our identity?

09:25.460 --> 09:28.820
So we take to religions.

09:32.640 --> 09:36.480
But religions have created nothing but fundamentalism.

09:39.920 --> 09:41.880
It is a blind faith.

09:44.740 --> 09:48.040
And all kinds of problems have brought up in the name of God.

09:56.680 --> 10:00.860
They are only money-oriented or power-oriented.

10:07.520 --> 10:10.940
They are not spirit-oriented.

10:14.880 --> 10:20.480
But in these modern times there are a lot of false gurus also

10:20.820 --> 10:24.440
who have come out to make money out of your simplicity.

10:36.040 --> 10:41.840
If it is a living process, how can you pay for it?

10:46.280 --> 10:48.240
Like this Mother Earth.

10:49.340 --> 10:52.860
How are we to pay Her for these flowers?

10:59.320 --> 11:02.900
Also some people say we have to suffer.

11:08.280 --> 11:11.940
There is no need to suffer at all.

11:16.920 --> 11:23.520
Imagine if God Almighty is the father of all the fathers,

11:23.520 --> 11:25.520
how can He want you to suffer or Him?

11:39.340 --> 11:41.360
He is your father,

11:41.600 --> 11:44.960
full of compassion,

11:45.500 --> 11:48.940
full of joy for you.

11:56.660 --> 12:00.140
I have seen there are some false people coming

12:00.460 --> 12:02.860
and teaching some mantras

12:03.240 --> 12:04.600
and things like that

12:04.880 --> 12:06.400
and some boys, I was surprised

12:06.620 --> 12:09.420
poor things were just going on saying some mantras.

12:25.740 --> 12:28.400
If it is coming from India,

12:29.400 --> 12:35.300
You should not believe that all that comems from India is good. Not at all.

12:39.880 --> 12:42.680
Be very careful.

12:42.960 --> 12:48.560
It is people who are trying to mesmerize your younger generation.

13:02.120 --> 13:03.960
As I have told you that

13:04.740 --> 13:09.040
you have to be the Spirit.

13:10.700 --> 13:14.740
That means it is an actualization.

13:15.680 --> 13:18.300
It is a happening

13:18.680 --> 13:21.440
of becoming.

13:32.160 --> 13:35.460
So it is not just a lecture or

13:35.800 --> 13:39.340
or a sermon or a mental process.

13:49.680 --> 13:52.220
But a happening within you.

13:52.480 --> 13:55.660
That you become something different.

14:04.080 --> 14:07.840
We see so many problems in this world these days

14:08.160 --> 14:11.560
You have no idea how much problematic it is

14:12.180 --> 14:15.520
in democratic countries.

14:24.000 --> 14:29.200
But it is happening in America which is supposed to be the greatest democratic country

14:29.480 --> 14:33.760
It is just full of idiotic and stupid people.

14:39.040 --> 14:45.080
It is surprising how they are taking life, for example

14:45.640 --> 14:49.160
they spend all their time in absolute, stupid, nonsencial

14:49.700 --> 14:53.320
idiotic things.

15:01.320 --> 15:05.640
I sometimes don´t understand how come

15:05.940 --> 15:10.040
human beings can become like that.

15:14.720 --> 15:16.840
Also tremendous level of

15:17.820 --> 15:22.600
an enterpreneour starts say a fashion.

15:22.980 --> 15:25.280
Say for example narrow pants.

15:37.860 --> 15:41.700
So they are all dressed up like that.

15:42.640 --> 15:46.800
Nobody has freedom to keep to their own dress.

15:53.480 --> 15:57.520
They all wear it and they get varicose veins.

16:04.700 --> 16:09.480
They wear it even then they get varicose veins.

16:11.340 --> 16:14.820
Then they develop some other nonsense.

16:19.900 --> 16:23.900
Like six-inches of a skirt for ladies.

16:30.340 --> 16:35.620
Even in the cold of England they are wearing that kind of a dress.

16:42.960 --> 16:44.880
They talk of individuality.

16:48.220 --> 16:50.220
Where is the individuality?

16:56.120 --> 17:01.520
They do really very stupid things please thank God you have escaped.

17:09.360 --> 17:14.000
They have got the freedom, alright, but no wisdom.

17:20.280 --> 17:30.240
And now it´s full of AIDS, full of schizofrenia, madness, lunacy, all kinds of funny diseases.

17:43.800 --> 17:47.480
Drugs of all kinds they are taking.

17:51.020 --> 17:54.880
It´s not only the children but even grown-ups in parties.

17:55.300 --> 17:58.020
They talk of drugs.

18:05.720 --> 18:09.380
They have not matured at all.

18:12.060 --> 18:15.900
I don´t say communism was the solution.

18:20.160 --> 18:22.620
But nor is democracy.

18:29.160 --> 18:31.660
Unless and until you have wisdom,

18:32.000 --> 18:34.980
both things can be very dangerous.

18:41.640 --> 18:48.320
Now they are selling all their junk which was not sold in their countries to you people here.

18:58.960 --> 19:08.240
Due to recession now they are going to Russia and all these places, even to India, to sell all their junk.

19:18.280 --> 19:20.360
But there is a solution

19:21.440 --> 19:23.420
to all these problems.

19:29.920 --> 19:33.500
This solution lies within yourself.

19:36.820 --> 19:40.580
You don´t have to go Moon,

19:42.180 --> 19:46.940
You don´t have to go to Jupiter to discover it.

19:56.540 --> 20:01.880
Most of the problems that are visible are due to human beings.

20:07.280 --> 20:11.720
Most of the human problems are beacuse of the subtle centers,

20:12.260 --> 20:15.420
within them are in trouble.

20:27.840 --> 20:31.120
When this Kundalini rises,

20:31.520 --> 20:34.300
She nourishes all these centers,

20:34.600 --> 20:37.580
interates them and connects you to this

20:38.140 --> 20:40.700
All-pervading Power.

20:58.400 --> 21:00.800
Because of these centers we suffer,

21:00.800 --> 21:05.280
physically, mentally, emotionally and spiritually.

21:16.820 --> 21:21.120
No doubt, with the ascend of Kundalini

21:21.880 --> 21:26.360
people have cured of their many incurable diseases.

21:39.280 --> 21:41.440
When the Kundalini comes

21:41.940 --> 21:44.100
out of your fontanel bone area,

21:44.740 --> 21:49.080
you can feel the cool breeze coming out of your head.

21:59.840 --> 22:04.800
This Kundalini is the reflection of the Holy Ghost within us.

22:17.040 --> 22:22.600
...described about God Almighty and His son.

22:25.660 --> 22:29.080
but nothing about the Mother.

22:31.120 --> 22:35.660
The third one is the Holy Ghost which is a dove.

22:42.000 --> 22:46.520
Symbolically it is alright, it is pure and it ascends.

22:52.080 --> 22:58.320
But in all other religions they have described  a Primordial Mother.

23:05.320 --> 23:09.520
This has happened because of Paul.

23:10.780 --> 23:13.020
He was a hater of women.

23:15.300 --> 23:18.340
And he never met Christ, all stories are told.

23:24.000 --> 23:29.860
He had killed so many christians and then he wanted to jump on the platform.

23:35.820 --> 23:37.900
And he chose Peter.

23:38.600 --> 23:44.500
as the person who will be anointed with the highest position

23:44.760 --> 23:49.000
in christian religion.

23:57.280 --> 24:00.640
Peter was the worst disciple of Christ.

24:06.200 --> 24:09.160
So Christ also said to Peter

24:09.160 --> 24:11.840
that a Satan will take you over.

24:18.720 --> 24:22.120
I was myself born in a christian family.

24:23.640 --> 24:26.360
And I asked my father: "Who is this Paul?"

24:30.460 --> 24:33.660
He was a realized soul my father,

24:34.200 --> 24:39.440
and he said: "He is a squatter."

24:42.160 --> 24:45.760
He has done a great harm to the West.

24:46.380 --> 24:48.680
by not respecting women.

24:57.560 --> 25:01.240
He did not respect the Mother of Christ.

25:03.940 --> 25:05.820
He calls her a woman.

25:09.260 --> 25:12.720
In Quran  Mohammed respects her very much.

25:18.520 --> 25:22.760
And said nobody should take any objection about her morality.

25:35.580 --> 25:42.300
This Paul´s turning of Christ´s life has really ruined the message of Christ.

25:57.380 --> 26:00.360
You find all these churches

26:00.600 --> 26:05.120
have become very money-oriented and power-oriented.

26:15.720 --> 26:21.460
So now after giving up communism you might jump onto these, any of them

26:22.120 --> 26:25.500
it´s very dangerous again.

26:34.300 --> 26:41.160
Even the Madonna was never a name given in the Bible to the mother of Christ.

26:50.120 --> 26:53.880
It came from the father religion.

26:54.720 --> 26:57.280
Which was before Christ.

27:08.200 --> 27:12.820
As a result the women in the West are extremely insecure.

27:20.280 --> 27:27.060
I was surprised, how they have to all the time please the men and please the children.

27:31.520 --> 27:39.300
And are really going into the complete waste of immorality.

27:46.340 --> 27:51.000
India politically and economically is a hopeless case. I agree.

27:58.940 --> 28:02.620
But the society is very well named.

28:10.920 --> 28:15.580
And women don´t have to be insecure in that society.

28:17.860 --> 28:21.240
For them their power is their chastity.

28:27.320 --> 28:30.020
Even in modern times.

28:34.180 --> 28:39.620
So to achieve that sense of security also we have to be the Spirit.

28:47.420 --> 28:49.580
First thing that happens to you

28:49.860 --> 28:53.080
you become thoughtlessly aware.

29:03.220 --> 29:06.600
It´s a new dimension in your awareness.

29:12.200 --> 29:19.980
There are thoughts which come to us from the past and the future.

29:22.240 --> 29:25.740
But we cannot be in the present.

29:28.220 --> 29:33.860
When the Kundalini rises she separates the thoughts.

29:36.100 --> 29:41.280
So we become thoughtless but fully aware.

29:47.020 --> 29:50.180
We jump into the present.

29:53.680 --> 29:56.560
Which is the reality.

29:58.940 --> 30:03.380
The past is finished and the future doesn´t exist.

30:07.480 --> 30:11.360
In that state you start growing spiritually.

30:18.840 --> 30:22.540
The Spirit is a universal being within you.

30:28.780 --> 30:30.840
It transcends

30:31.200 --> 30:36.060
all barriers that we have created by our mental activity.

30:45.560 --> 30:48.760
Of ritualism, fundamentalism, all kinds of isms.

30:57.660 --> 31:02.780
You realize that all these religions were born on the same tree of spirituality.

31:03.160 --> 31:07.920
These people have cut them and are fighting with the dead flowers.

31:25.040 --> 31:28.020
In the state of thoughtless awareness

31:28.260 --> 31:30.240
you feel your peace within yourself.

31:34.740 --> 31:36.900
This is the peace we are seeking.

31:39.000 --> 31:41.000
People talk of peace,

31:44.640 --> 31:49.120
have big arguments and conferences but there is no peace within themselves.

32:00.340 --> 32:03.220
They have been given awards and this, that.

32:03.680 --> 32:09.140
But I have seen they are very hot-tempered people.

32:16.780 --> 32:18.400
So by your ascend

32:19.760 --> 32:22.160
you become a peaceful personality,

32:22.400 --> 32:25.600
relaxed personality, satisfied personality.

32:36.460 --> 32:39.240
And you become wise nad discreet.

32:47.780 --> 32:51.100
Because you see the reality.

32:54.720 --> 32:57.320
And you feel the totality.

33:00.240 --> 33:04.320
When this Kundalini pierces thought the fontanel bone area,

33:04.320 --> 33:07.500
you start feeling cool breeze on your fingertips.

33:17.660 --> 33:20.200
This is the All-pervading power.

33:28.260 --> 33:32.200
Which in Quran is called as Ruh.

33:34.380 --> 33:36.620
In sanskrit as Paramachaitanya.

33:39.900 --> 33:46.220
Your attention becomes enlightened and innocent.

33:48.820 --> 33:52.520
You innocence is never lost.

33:55.980 --> 33:59.080
It is always there.

34:00.380 --> 34:06.240
Only thing, because of your so called freedom there are some clouds.

34:11.080 --> 34:17.240
But when Kundalini rises and connects you to the All-pervading power

34:18.940 --> 34:22.140
you become innocent, your eyes ecome innocent.

34:32.460 --> 34:36.120
You know the Absolute truth on your finger tips,

34:41.440 --> 34:43.280
even the realized children can tell you

34:44.600 --> 34:46.760
what´s wrong with your centers.

34:52.900 --> 34:56.900
Not that you can feel your own centers, that´s self-knowledge,

34:56.900 --> 34:58.940
but also the centers of others.

35:07.580 --> 35:09.580
So you develop a new dimension

35:09.880 --> 35:13.920
in your awareness of collective consciousness.

35:21.940 --> 35:26.800
Ultimately you develop the powers to raise the Kundalini of others.

35:38.640 --> 35:42.500
As one enlightened candle can enlighten many candles.

35:43.920 --> 35:48.020
The life becomes absolutely blissful.

35:51.600 --> 35:54.700
And you jump into the ocean of joy.

35:58.240 --> 35:59.520
Joy has no duality.

36:00.940 --> 36:03.020
of happiness and unhappiness.

36:12.280 --> 36:15.280
It is the experience of joy, you feel it.

36:24.620 --> 36:27.260
Sahajayoga is working in 55 nations,

36:33.940 --> 36:37.120
so many have been cured.

36:37.960 --> 36:41.500
so many have now the powers,

36:41.900 --> 36:47.440
but I have never seen them fighting, quarreling,

36:55.320 --> 37:00.560
All full of humour and enjoyment.

37:07.740 --> 37:10.780
What a different type of life.

37:15.960 --> 37:18.360
That´s what is for you.

37:23.880 --> 37:30.540
You have to achieve it without any difficulties.

37:33.820 --> 37:36.240
It is very, very simple.

37:38.400 --> 37:41.000
Sahaja means "born with you,"

37:43.760 --> 37:48.560
is the right to be united, that is yoga, with this All-pervading power.

37:57.880 --> 38:00.740
For which you don´t pay.

38:02.900 --> 38:05.060
But it is a collective happening

38:05.760 --> 38:07.680
it´s a collective organism,

38:13.940 --> 38:15.860
so you have to be collective.

38:16.820 --> 38:20.080
If one nail is cut out, it doesn´t grow.

38:26.860 --> 38:33.960
Now see how Germans and Austrians have come to your town

38:34.320 --> 38:36.720
and arranged this program.

38:47.640 --> 38:50.640
How so many English going to Russia.

38:54.840 --> 38:58.760
Like there is one finger which has some pain, the whole body

39:00.120 --> 39:05.040
goes to it to get it alright.

39:17.380 --> 39:20.180
So it will take hardly about ten minutes from you

39:21.240 --> 39:22.920
to get your realization.

39:29.680 --> 39:31.840
But there are three conditions.

39:35.180 --> 39:36.700
Which are very simple.

39:41.100 --> 39:45.160
The first one is that

39:45.880 --> 39:50.360
you should not feel guilty at all.

39:55.500 --> 39:58.140
It´s a fashion nowadays to feel guilty.

40:02.120 --> 40:06.360
After all, you are human beings and human beings all make mistakes.

40:07.020 --> 40:10.240
You are not God.

40:16.240 --> 40:20.100
If you make mistakes, let´s face it, why feel guilty?

40:28.280 --> 40:32.560
By feeling guilty, this centre here on the left side

40:32.940 --> 40:35.080
goes out of order.

40:40.600 --> 40:43.800
And physically also you may suffer from angina,

40:45.640 --> 40:49.800
or from spondylitis or from lethargic organs all over the body.

41:04.260 --> 41:07.540
Don´t believe people who tell you you are sinners.

41:09.800 --> 41:13.320
They are the greatest sinners who tell you like that.

41:17.160 --> 41:21.640
After all you are human beings, you are at the epitomy of evolution.

41:31.220 --> 41:32.820
The second condition is

41:33.860 --> 41:38.040
that you have to forgive evryone in general.

41:47.000 --> 41:51.640
Logically whether you forgive or you don´t forgive, you don´t do anything.

41:54.940 --> 41:56.620
But if you don´t forgive,

41:57.020 --> 42:00.620
than you play into wrong hands and torture yourself.

42:08.300 --> 42:13.080
So you don´t even have to think about them, you have to just

42:14.200 --> 42:19.240
in general, say " I forgive everyone," it´s nonsense.

42:24.600 --> 42:27.240
Also it is a myth.

42:33.900 --> 42:37.480
Now there is a center within us on the optic chiasm which is like this.

42:38.620 --> 42:40.620
Closed.

42:49.920 --> 42:52.800
And if you don´t forgive,

42:53.040 --> 42:55.500
then it doesn´t open.

42:55.980 --> 42:58.540
But if you forgive, it opens like this.

43:02.620 --> 43:06.020
You feel much lighter and

43:07.260 --> 43:09.180
Kundalini may pass through.

43:19.220 --> 43:22.740
All your life you tortured yourself by not forgiving.

43:23.720 --> 43:26.600
And at this moment you will miss the great point

43:27.300 --> 43:29.460
of achieving your realization.

43:43.540 --> 43:45.300
Now the third condition is

43:46.000 --> 43:50.280
that you have to have full faith in yourself,

43:50.340 --> 43:54.980
full confidence that you will all get your realization tonight.

44:07.440 --> 44:13.560
It sounds fantastic but you are fantastic.

44:13.980 --> 44:20.720
You don´t know yourself. Once you know yourself, you will be amazed,

44:20.980 --> 44:23.680
how many powers you have.

44:25.740 --> 44:29.680
What you can do to yourself and to  the whole world.

44:36.260 --> 44:42.200
Unless and until this microphone is connected to the mains, it has no identity, it has no meaning.

44:54.680 --> 44:57.640
But as soon as you are connected to the mains,

44:58.580 --> 45:00.940
you know what you are.

45:06.980 --> 45:09.500
These are the three conditions

45:10.120 --> 45:11.960
I hope you will fulfill.

45:23.580 --> 45:26.540
As it is I think you are very sensible people,

45:27.620 --> 45:30.960
the way you have elected your president,

45:40.760 --> 45:42.600
the whole  world knows that.

45:47.420 --> 45:51.020
So now those who do not want to have their realization,

45:53.780 --> 45:57.760
should know that I cannot force it on you.

46:05.460 --> 46:07.620
Because I respect your freedom.

46:11.640 --> 46:13.160
It´s a last judgement,

46:13.440 --> 46:16.380
you have to judge yourself.

46:20.560 --> 46:23.920
In Quran it is said that at the time of resurrection

46:24.720 --> 46:26.240
your hands will speak.

46:26.680 --> 46:30.060
They give a witness against you.

46:40.000 --> 46:43.440
And these hands will tell you what´s wrong with you and

46:43.640 --> 46:46.280
what´s wrong with others.

46:50.260 --> 46:52.980
And if you know how to correct your centers,

46:52.980 --> 46:54.980
you can correct yourself

46:55.820 --> 46:57.660
and you can correct others.

47:07.620 --> 47:11.940
Those who do not want to have realization, should leave the hall.

47:16.680 --> 47:22.540
Of course, Sahajayoga is not meant for idiots and stupid people.

47:27.380 --> 47:30.500
And it´s not meant for  arrogant people either.

47:31.020 --> 47:39.100
Also for people who are involved in some sort of an ideology or

47:42.860 --> 47:45.620
some sort of blind faith.

47:58.560 --> 48:02.800
Again I request those who do not want to have their self-realization,

48:03.300 --> 48:05.140
they should leave the hall.

48:28.680 --> 48:31.720
You have to be pleasently placed to yourself,

48:37.860 --> 48:38.580
now please

48:39.280 --> 48:44.000
you have to remove your shoes,

48:44.680 --> 48:46.760
because this Mother Earth also

48:47.140 --> 48:49.300
helps us to suck in our problems.

49:14.080 --> 49:18.000
Now the left and the right are two powers,

49:18.540 --> 49:19.980
one is for your desire

49:20.300 --> 49:21.900
and another for action.

49:32.600 --> 49:36.120
So you have to put both your feet apart from each other

49:36.420 --> 49:38.680
and sit comfortably.

49:44.520 --> 49:48.280
You don´t have to go to the Himalayas and stand on your head.

49:54.180 --> 49:57.700
You will get your realization in your seats tonight.

50:03.660 --> 50:08.120
So now please put your left hand

50:08.720 --> 50:13.340
towards Me on your left hip or left.

50:24.300 --> 50:27.500
Beacuse this is suggestive or symbolic that you

50:27.580 --> 50:31.220
desire to have your self-realization.

50:38.160 --> 50:42.180
You have to have Pure desire.

50:44.520 --> 50:50.040
The right hand we use for nourishing our centers on the lefthand side of ourselves.

50:56.820 --> 50:59.500
This we do it only

50:59.860 --> 51:02.580
for tonight you don´t have to do it later.

51:07.480 --> 51:13.140
So now please put your right hand on your heart.

51:13.140 --> 51:15.140
Somebody will show it.

51:26.960 --> 51:29.660
In the heart resides the Spirit.

51:33.140 --> 51:36.380
If you become the Spirit, in the light of your Spirit,

51:36.680 --> 51:39.220
you become your own master.

51:47.600 --> 51:51.020
So you have to take your right hand

51:51.340 --> 51:56.280
in the upper portion of your abdomen on the left hand side.

52:05.060 --> 52:08.500
This is the center of your mastery.

52:11.720 --> 52:17.060
Which is created by all the great Prophets.

52:25.460 --> 52:28.480
It has to be enlightened.

52:29.520 --> 52:36.140
So now you have to take your right hand in the lower portion of your abdomen on the lefthand side.

52:41.400 --> 52:48.060
This is the center of Pure divine knowledge.

52:56.780 --> 52:59.640
We will know about it later on,

53:00.080 --> 53:04.860
how it caters to the Divine knowledge.

53:22.820 --> 53:28.720
Now please raise your hand in the upper portion of your abdomen,

53:37.420 --> 53:39.440
now on your heart.

53:41.240 --> 53:50.000
Now in the corner of your neck and shoulder and turn your head to your right.

53:58.180 --> 54:04.840
I have already told you what happens to you when this center is out of care.

54:09.660 --> 54:17.080
Now take your right hand on your forehead across and put out your head.

54:24.600 --> 54:30.120
This is the center for forgiving everyone in general.

54:36.640 --> 54:39.480
Now please take back your right hand

54:39.480 --> 54:42.660
on the backside of your head and push back.

54:43.000 --> 54:45.100
as far as possible.

54:53.520 --> 55:02.720
This center, without feeling guilty, without counting your mistakes, just for your satisfaction.

55:15.380 --> 55:17.540
You have to ask for forgiveness.

55:17.860 --> 55:20.180
From this Divine power.

55:26.440 --> 55:29.620
Now the last center is important.

55:32.200 --> 55:34.760
Please stretch your palm fully.

55:39.620 --> 55:45.720
Put the center of your palm on the fontanel bone area

55:45.960 --> 55:50.040
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

55:59.860 --> 56:03.480
Push back your fingers as far as possible.

56:07.560 --> 56:09.480
Press it hard,

56:09.900 --> 56:15.940
move your scalp and move it seven times slowly, clockwise.

56:30.340 --> 56:32.900
That´s all you have to do.

56:39.540 --> 56:42.100
Now we have to close our eyes,

56:45.180 --> 56:49.660
before that please see that both your feet are apart from each other

56:57.240 --> 57:00.680
Put the left hand toward Me like this.

57:06.620 --> 57:08.600
Right hand on the heart.

57:11.600 --> 57:14.880
Do not concentrate, do not pressurize your mind.

57:20.940 --> 57:23.740
Everything will work out spontaneously.

57:29.280 --> 57:30.640
Now close your eyes.

57:30.640 --> 57:33.300
And please don´t open them till I tell you.

57:44.360 --> 57:47.480
Here you have to ask Me a fundamental question

57:47.740 --> 57:49.660
about yourself three times.

57:50.600 --> 57:53.080
You can call Me Mother or Shri Mataji.

58:04.180 --> 58:06.660
Please ask three times in your heart.

58:10.360 --> 58:11.960
Mother, am I the Spirit?

58:19.900 --> 58:22.780
I have told you, when you become the Spirit,

58:24.740 --> 58:26.580
you become your own master.

58:36.740 --> 58:42.020
So take your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen on the left hand side

58:42.020 --> 58:42.900
press it hard

58:43.300 --> 58:51.140
and here ask another fundamental question about yourself to Me.

58:59.040 --> 59:03.520
Ask a question: "Mother, am I my own master?"

59:03.820 --> 59:06.020
Three times.

59:17.740 --> 59:21.180
I have already told you that I respect your freedom.

59:21.500 --> 59:25.080
I cannot force pure knowledge on you.

59:40.940 --> 59:43.000
Take out your hand

59:45.780 --> 59:50.380
on the lower portion of your abdomen on the left hand side.

59:59.140 --> 01:00:03.320
Here you have to ask for Pure knowledge.

01:00:08.660 --> 01:00:13.520
Here ask 6 times because this center has got 6 petals.

01:00:13.900 --> 01:00:18.160
Mother please give me Pure knowledge.

01:00:43.840 --> 01:00:46.400
As soon as you ask for Pure knowledge,

01:00:46.540 --> 01:00:51.100
the Kundalini starts rising and we have to nourish the upper centers

01:00:51.760 --> 01:00:53.520
with our full confidence.

01:01:05.180 --> 01:01:10.780
So now raise your right hand to the upper portion of your abdomen

01:01:11.340 --> 01:01:14.240
on the left hand side and press it hard

01:01:14.360 --> 01:01:18.840
here you ahve to say with full confidence 10 times,

01:01:19.580 --> 01:01:23.060
Mother, I am my own master.

01:01:56.400 --> 01:02:01.200
I alreday told you that you are not this body, this mind, this ego

01:02:01.540 --> 01:02:03.220
these conditionings but

01:02:03.420 --> 01:02:05.340
you are the Pure Spirit.

01:02:16.460 --> 01:02:19.660
So now raise your right hand on your heart and say

01:02:19.660 --> 01:02:21.500
with full confidence 12 times

01:02:22.000 --> 01:02:24.820
Mother, I am the Pure Spirit.

01:02:42.660 --> 01:02:44.820
This All-pervading power is the

01:02:45.300 --> 01:02:48.700
ocean of knowledge.

01:02:54.580 --> 01:03:00.160
It is the ocean of joy and blessings.

01:03:03.600 --> 01:03:10.960
But above all it is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:03:12.440 --> 01:03:15.560
Whatever misteakes you might have committed,

01:03:20.640 --> 01:03:26.480
it can be easily dissolved by this power of forgiveness.

01:03:34.340 --> 01:03:42.060
So now forgive yourself and raise your hand to the border of your neck and turn your head to the right.

01:03:55.160 --> 01:03:59.280
Here you have to say with full confidence 16 times

01:04:00.680 --> 01:04:03.560
Mother I am not guilty at all.

01:04:17.500 --> 01:04:20.060
I have already told you that logically

01:04:20.060 --> 01:04:22.440
whether you forgive or you don´t forgive

01:04:22.640 --> 01:04:24.160
you don´t do anything.

01:04:32.000 --> 01:04:34.620
But you torture yourself.

01:04:39.960 --> 01:04:48.920
At this junction if you don´t forgive, the center won´t open and Kundalini won´t pass.

01:05:05.940 --> 01:05:11.180
So please forgive all of them in general, not thinking about them.

01:05:19.320 --> 01:05:24.880
Now raise your right hand on the forehead across and put your head down

01:05:25.000 --> 01:05:29.040
and here you have to say from your heart, not how many times

01:05:29.360 --> 01:05:34.520
Mother, I forgive everyone in general.

01:05:52.300 --> 01:05:55.180
Now without feeling guilty

01:05:55.180 --> 01:05:56.940
without counting your mistakes

01:05:57.740 --> 01:05:59.660
just for your satisfaction,

01:06:00.740 --> 01:06:05.480
you have to ask forgiveness from the Divine Power.

01:06:24.740 --> 01:06:27.540
Take your hand on the backside of your head

01:06:28.140 --> 01:06:30.400
and push back your head

01:06:30.560 --> 01:06:32.980
and here with full confidence from your heart, not how many times -

01:06:35.240 --> 01:06:40.380
you have to say - Divine Power if I have done wrong,

01:06:40.800 --> 01:06:44.000
knowingly or unknowingly, please forogive me.

01:07:05.660 --> 01:07:07.960
The last center is important.

01:07:08.260 --> 01:07:10.860
Where you have to stretch your palm fully

01:07:11.240 --> 01:07:13.240
and put the center of your palm

01:07:13.240 --> 01:07:15.180
on top of the fontanel bone area

01:07:15.440 --> 01:07:17.920
which is a soft bone in your childhood

01:07:36.040 --> 01:07:40.680
Put down your head and push back your fingers so there is sufficient pressure on your scalp.

01:07:54.100 --> 01:07:57.460
Here again I cannot force self-realization on you

01:07:57.460 --> 01:07:58.900
you have to ask for it.

01:07:59.560 --> 01:08:04.400
So move your hand seven times clockwise

01:08:04.400 --> 01:08:10.060
say from your heart - Mother please give me my self-realization.

01:08:39.500 --> 01:08:42.160
Please bend your head.

01:08:44.240 --> 01:08:45.840
Push back your fingers.

01:09:27.620 --> 01:09:30.740
Take down your hands please and open your eyes.

01:09:38.900 --> 01:09:41.700
Now please put both your hands towards Me.

01:09:52.100 --> 01:09:54.740
And don´t think.

01:09:59.720 --> 01:10:02.600
Now put the right hand towards Me like this.

01:10:09.980 --> 01:10:12.460
Put out your head and see for yourself

01:10:13.020 --> 01:10:19.180
if there si cool or hot breeze coming out of your fontanel bone area.

01:10:36.360 --> 01:10:43.280
You shouldn´t put your hand on top of your head, but away from it.

01:10:52.900 --> 01:10:54.820
Put your left hand towards Me...

01:10:56.800 --> 01:11:00.080
not on top, a bit away or you cannot feel it at all.

01:11:06.140 --> 01:11:08.620
Please put your left hand towards Me.

01:11:08.620 --> 01:11:10.800
Bend your head and see for yourself

01:11:10.920 --> 01:11:15.640
if there is a cool or a hot breeze coming out of your fontanel bone area.

01:11:31.740 --> 01:11:37.200
If you have not forgiven yourself or others, it will be hot.

01:11:42.420 --> 01:11:44.520
Now forgive.

01:11:46.260 --> 01:11:51.860
Lastly again, put right hand towards me, put down your head and see for yourself

01:11:52.080 --> 01:11:57.000
if there is a cool breeze coming out of your head.

01:12:16.660 --> 01:12:19.300
Please bend your heads.

01:12:24.720 --> 01:12:28.640
Now please raise your both your hands towards the sky like this.

01:12:36.700 --> 01:12:40.340
Push back your head upward.

01:12:47.440 --> 01:12:50.560
Ask any out of these three questions three times.

01:13:01.400 --> 01:13:04.260
Please ask

01:13:04.260 --> 01:13:08.660
Mother, is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?

01:13:12.920 --> 01:13:20.240
Mother is this the All-pervading power of God´s Love?

01:13:21.640 --> 01:13:34.520
Mother, is this the Paramachaytanya? Or Ruh?

01:13:34.520 --> 01:13:39.360
Any of these questions you can ask three times.

01:13:49.180 --> 01:13:51.180
Now please take down your hands.

01:13:57.720 --> 01:14:00.120
Put your hands like this towards Me.

01:14:04.040 --> 01:14:06.760
And don´t think.

01:14:09.860 --> 01:14:13.780
Those who have felt cool or hot breeze on their fingertips,

01:14:14.820 --> 01:14:16.500
or on their heads, palms,

01:14:17.400 --> 01:14:19.480
or out of the fontanel bone area,

01:14:20.260 --> 01:14:23.860
please raise your hands.

01:14:44.660 --> 01:14:48.220
All of you. All of you.

01:14:50.080 --> 01:14:52.680
May God bless you.

01:14:54.480 --> 01:14:56.320
Except for one or two people.
